-Pictures of how it is coming along! -I don't know =S

-If you want to be the host you don't have to host until the progress is 90%
Extras:
-I will not spend months on this! i can make a good server out of my friends source! -If i have to restart... i will get someone too help fix my errors
Items that are "made!"
